{"tid":1248774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日圍警總人數夠 唔好有機會令自己人受傷 又係時候set deadline","createTime":"2019-06-21T14:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T15:02:27.000Z","uid":33577,"like":57,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"771dce5241cfb9a6bcebd82d6be27309336cad13","tid":1248774,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"既然4點訴求佢唔肯回應<br />\n即管再set個deadline俾佢回應<br />\n底線係要成立獨立委員會調查警察濫權、暴力<br />\n同埋速龍嘅制服問題，要求問責<br />\n<br />\n今日圍警總人數夠曬 癱瘓到政府部門運作<br />\n已經展示到我哋而家係<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有實力</span></span>影響政府運作<br />\n圍警總有一定風險 趁未有衝突之前可以繼續保全實力<br />\n俾一個weekend時間佢 盧偉聰唔回應 <br />\n星期一先再圍佢老母 再升級 癱瘓政府不同機關運作 工都唔俾佢返<br />\n<br />\n天黑、深夜時分我哋同警犬鬥無優勢，隨時損兵折將<br />\n亦唔需要再擔心有白癡會衝狗屋<br />\n<br />\n大家意下如何？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死線係星期日2359</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1ed27f31cf1a1af0d3bee41051b929d885a0ca70","tid":1248774,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5f134f0be2fc7f5b408d2e14f7ffc607a9c152","tid":1248774,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac69c7fb9668a826c4f511fd4a426519ebece80a","tid":1248774,"uid":136640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"Deadline完點升級？"},{"pid":"6151b5abad6f2a1c2e4a971d312f8ab4863ad5d5","tid":1248774,"uid":33577,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:16:45.000Z","msg":"同佢僵持無意思<br />\n俾個理由口實派 而家示威者激情理性均全 要求合理<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日2359前要有回覆</span></span>"},{"pid":"3ecf500cecb8c8ee3ebb41ec1aced80f0dd77910","tid":1248774,"uid":33577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ac69c7fb9